#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:4
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:6
msgid "Welcome to Blender, the free and open source 3D creation suite."
msgstr "欢迎使用Blender这一免费开源的3D创作套件。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:8
msgid "Blender can be used to create 3D visualizations such as still images, video, and real-time interactive video games."
msgstr "Blender可以创作多种3D视觉内容，比如图像、视频以及实时交互的视频游戏等。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:10
msgid "Blender is well suited to individuals and small studios who benefit from its unified pipeline and responsive development process."
msgstr "Blender 非常适合于独立开发者以及中小型工作室，它高度统一的工作流以及非常可靠的开发过程可以让所有人从中受益。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:13
msgid ""
"Blender is a cross-platform application, running on Linux, macOS, and MS-Windows systems. Blender also has a relatively small memory and drive "
"requirements compared to other 3D creation suites. Its interface uses OpenGL to provide a consistent experience across all supported hardware and "
"platforms."
msgstr ""
"Blender是一款跨平台的应用工具，可以在Linux、macOS以及MS-Windows系统下运行。与其他3D建模工具相比，Blender对内存和驱动的需求更低。使用了OpenGL技术的接口即便"
"跨越所有支持的硬件与平台都能提供相当稳定的用户体验。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:19
msgid "Blender 2.5 with a Big Buck Bunny scene open."
msgstr "使用Blender 2.5 版打开的大雄兔(Big Buck Bunny)电影场景。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:23
msgid "Who uses Blender?"
msgstr "谁在使用Blender？"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:25
msgid ""
"Blender has a wide variety of tools making it suitable for almost any sort of media production. People and studios around the world use it for hobby "
"projects, commercials, feature films, games and other interactive applications like kiosks, games and scientific research."
msgstr ""
"Blender有一套非常丰富的工具集，因此几乎可以适用于所有类型的媒体产品。全世界的工作室与开发者们都把它用在各种各样的项目中，包括业余作品、商业化的产品、电"
"影、游戏以及其他互动应用比如多功能信息栏，游戏以及科学研究。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:29
msgid "Check out the `User Stories page <https://www.blender.org/features/user-stories/>`__ on the Blender website for more examples."
msgstr "去Blender的站点上看看吧！那里有 `讲述使用者的故事 <https://www.blender.org/features/user-stories/>`__ 。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:34
msgid "Key Features"
msgstr "主要功能"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:36
msgid ""
"Blender is a fully integrated 3D content creation suite, offering a broad range of essential tools, including :doc:`Modeling </modeling/introduction>`, :"
"doc:`Rendering </render/introduction>`, :doc:`Animation </animation/introduction>`, :doc:`Video Editing </editors/vse/index>`, :doc:`VFX </editors/"
"movie_clip_editor/index>`, :doc:`Compositing </compositing/introduction>`, :doc:`Texturing </editors/uv_image/uv/overview>`, :doc:`Rigging </rigging/"
"introduction>`, many types of :doc:`Simulations </physics/introduction>`, and :doc:`Game Creation </game_engine/introduction>`."
msgstr ""
"Blender是一套完整集成了3D内容创作的套件，全面提供了必要的创作工具包括 :doc:`建模 </modeling/introduction>`, :doc:`渲染 </render/introduction>`, :doc:`动"
"画 </animation/introduction>`, :doc:`视频编辑 </editors/vse/index>`, :doc:`特效后期 </editors/movie_clip_editor/index>`, :doc:`合成 </compositing/"
"introduction>`, :doc:`制作贴图 </editors/uv_image/uv/overview>`, :doc:`骨骼蒙皮 </rigging/introduction>`, 多种多样的 :doc:`物理模拟 </physics/"
"introduction>`, 以及 :doc:`游戏制作 </game_engine/introduction>` 。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:47
msgid "Cross platform, with an OpenGL GUI that is uniform on all major platforms (and customizable with Python scripts)."
msgstr "跨平台，使用了OpenGL的GUI可以在所有主流平台上都表现出一致的显示效果（并且可通过Python脚本来自定义界面）。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:48
msgid "High-quality 3D architecture enabling fast and efficient creation workflow."
msgstr "高质量的3D架构，带来了快速且高效的工作流。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:49
msgid "Excellent community support from `forums <http://blenderartists.org/forum/>`__ and :ref:`IRC <irc-channels>`."
msgstr "来自 `论坛 <http://BlenderArtists.org>`__ 和 :ref:`在线聊天室 <irc-channels>` 出色的社区支持。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:50
msgid "Small executable size, optionally portable."
msgstr "体积小巧，便于分发。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:52
msgid "You can download the latest version of Blender `here <https://www.blender.org/download/>`__."
msgstr "你可以在 `这里 <http://www.blender.org/download/>`_ 下载最新版Blender。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:56
msgid "A rendered image being post-processed."
msgstr "正在经历后期处理的已渲染图像。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:58
msgid ""
"Blender makes it possible to perform a wide range of tasks, and it may seem daunting when first trying to grasp the basics. However, with a bit of "
"motivation and the right learning material, it is possible to familiarize yourself with Blender after a few hours of practice."
msgstr ""
"Blender可以胜任多种多样的任务，也许初次上手会让你产生那么一点点胆怯。但是，只需要再来上一点点的兴趣以及正确的学习材料，几个小时之后你就会彻底和Blender熟络"
"起来啦！（顺带一提，这里有Blender中文视频集：http://i.youku.com/u/UMTgzMTA0NDc2MA）"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:62
msgid ""
"This manual is a good start though it serves more as a reference. There are also many online video tutorials from specialized websites, and several books "
"and training DVDs available in the `Blender Store <https://store.blender.org/>`__ and on the `Blender Cloud <https://cloud.blender.org/>`__."
msgstr ""
"本手册尽管只是作为一份参考，但它同时也是一个良好的开端。在同一时间也有许多来自专业网站的在线视频教程、书籍以及教学DVD在  `Blender 网店 <https://store."
"blender.org/>`__ 和 `Blender 云服务 <https://cloud.blender.org/>`__ 上等着你。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:67
msgid ""
"Despite everything Blender can do, it remains a tool. Great artists do not create masterpieces by pressing buttons or manipulating brushes, but by "
"learning and practicing subjects such as human anatomy, composition, lighting, animation principles, etc."
msgstr ""
"尽管Blender可以办到几乎所有的事情，但它仍然只是一个工具。再伟大的艺术大师也不可能仅仅通过按几个按钮或者随便刷几笔就做出惊人的艺术作品来，相反，他们也要经"
"过大量的学习与训练，包括：人体结构，合成，灯光，动画原理等等等等。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:71
msgid ""
"3D creation software such as Blender have the added technical complexity and jargon associated with the underlying technologies. Terms like UV maps, "
"materials, shaders, meshes, and \"subsurf\" are the mediums of the digital artist, and understanding them, even broadly, will help you to use Blender to "
"its best."
msgstr ""
"像Blender这样的3D内容创作工具软件在深层的技术背后还有着不少技术难点以及行业术语。一些专用术语比如UV贴图、材质、着色器、网格、细分曲面等都是数字艺术家表达"
"思想的媒介，理解它们，运用它们，你才能将Blender用到极致。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about/introduction.rst:76
msgid ""
"So keep reading this manual, learn the great tool that Blender is, keep your mind open to other artistic and technological areas and you too can become a "
"great artist."
msgstr "那么接下来请继续阅读这套手册，学习更多Blender里面的工具功能，放开思维与其他艺术家和科技领域融为一体，总有一天你也能成为一位伟大的艺术家。"
